  <div class="width-container">

    <div>

      <div class="line">
        <div class="container left">
          <h6>
            WEB Development
          </h6>

          <p>
            We are a Ruby on Rails agency that practices agile development to build your site or app.
            Transparency, flexibility and product quality are the key, so we designed our collaborative
            processes around test-driven development, strict unit tests, rigorous peer reviews and QA
