            team. If your project needs more resources we can allocate a full team or individuals to
            help
            you with your project. We apply agile methodology and follow a test-driven development
            process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="line">
        <div class="container left">
          <h6>
            Design and UX
          </h6>

          <p>
