            intuitive,
            clever and elegant user experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="line-icon right"></span>
      </div>

      <div class="line">
        <span class="line-icon left"></span>

        <div class="container right">
          <h6>
            Brand identity
          </h6>

